                               String prot,
                               String source,
                               String destination,
                               String options,
                               FirewallRule.Table table)
                                        throws Exception
        Parse the parameters of an IPTablesLine an create a FirewallRule
        Parameters:
        target - "ACCEPT" or "DROP"
        prot - the protocol (tcp, udp, all)
        source - the source ip address with or without /mask
        destination - the destination ip address with or without /mask
        options - the options
        Returns:
        the FirewallRule related to the parameters
        Throws:
        Exception
